brandedFoodCategory: Croissants, Sweet Rolls, Muffins & Other Pastries
ingredients: BASE & FILLING: ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, ASCORBIC ACID [ADDED AS A DOUGH CONDITIONER], THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, ENZYME, FOLIC ACID), GLUCOSE SYRUP, MARGARINE (SOYBEAN OIL, PALM OIL, WATER, SALT, WHEY [MILK], VEGETABLE MONOGLYCERIDES, SOY LECITHIN, NATURAL FLAVOR, ANNATTO EXTRACT [COLOR], TURMERIC [ADDED FOR COLOR], VITAMIN A PALMITATE, VITAMIN D3), SWEETENED CONDENSED MILK (MILK INGREDIENTS [WHEY], SUGAR, LACTOSE), COCONUT (COCONUT, SODIUM METABISULFITE [PRESERVATIVE]), GRANULATED CANE SUGAR, WATER, WHOLE WHEAT FLOUR, VEGETABLE SHORTENING (PALM OIL, SOYBEAN OIL), HONEY, MOLASSES, BAKING SODA, SALT, AMMONIUM BICARBONATE, LIQUID WHOLE EGG. TOPPINGS: BUTTERSCOTCH CHIPS (SUGAR, PALM KERNEL OIL, WHOLE MILK POWDER, NONFAT DRY MILK POWDER, COCOA POWDER, SOY LECITHIN [AN EMULSIFIER], NATURAL FLAVOR, PAPRIKA EXTRACT [ADDED FOR COLOR]), SEMI-SWEET CHOCOLATE (SUGAR, UNSWEETENED CHOCOLATE, COCOA BUTTER, DEXTROSE, SOY LECITHIN [AN EMULSIFIER], NATURAL VANILLA), COCONUT (COCONUT, SODIUM METABISULFITE [PRESERVATIVE]), PECANS.
